casebody.data:
Phillip D. KLINE, petitioner,
v.
KANSAS DISCIPLINARY ADMINISTRATOR. No. 13-1104. Supreme Court of the United States April 28, 2014.

Case below, 298 Kan. 96, 311 P.3d 321.

Motion of Eagle Forum Education & Legal Defense Fund, Inc., et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Motion of National Lawyers' Association, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Kansas denied.
